    http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4

    ValueWithAttributes LocationCode

      • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4:StringTiny
        • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4:LocationCode

      • Description

        Location code is city, stateProvence, or country code

    • Example XML

      <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>

<LocationCode city="Lancaster" codeContext="Example String Value" country="US" stateProvince="PA" xmlns="http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4">Example String Value</LocationCode>

      Example JSON

      {
  "LocationCode" : {
    "value" : "Example String Value",
    "city" : "Lancaster",
    "stateProvince" : "PA",
    "country" : "US",
    "codeContext" : "Example String Value"
  }
}
